### Get all flights
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/flights

### Create new flight
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/flights
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "flightCode": "VN123",
    "route": "Hà Nội - Hồ Chí Minh",
    "departureTime": "2025-10-05T08:30:00.000Z",
    "arrivalTime": "2025-10-05T10:30:00.000Z",
    "totalSeats": 180,
    "availableSeats": 180
}

