### Update flight (thay :id bằng ID thực tế trong MongoDB)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/flights/YOUR_FLIGHT_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "totalSeats": 200,
    "availableSeats": 180
}

